STEPS TO RUN THE JAVA MULTI CLIENT CHAT APP

1. RUN THE SERVER FILE
2. PIN THE CONSOLE OF SERVER
3. RUN THE CLIENT FILE MULTIPLE TIME TIMES TO VIEW THE MULTI CLIENT VIEW
4. OPEN MULTIPLE CONSOLE AND SELECT DIFFERENT CLIENT ON EACH CONSOLE FROM THE CONSOLE DROPDOWN MENU
5. TYPE THE NAME OF CLIENTS ON CLIENT CONSOLE TO ENTER GROUP CHAT AND CHECK THE OUTPUT ON EACH CONSOLE
6. EACH TIME A NEW CLIENT ENTERS THE GROUP CHAT SERVER WILL BE NOTIFIED
7. WHEN A CLIENT CHAT IT WILL BE VISIBLE TO ALL THE OTHER CLIENTS PART OF THE CHAT GROUP